My First Test is a simple '''Hello World''' project hosted on [GitHub]. The project is described as a dark minimal page with centered text, built using basic web development technologies.

== Overview ==
The project is a basic implementation of a web page, focusing on simplicity and ease of use. It is designed to be a starting point for further development and experimentation.

=== Features ===
The project features a minimalistic design, with a focus on '''HTML''' and '''CSS'''. The page is centered, with a dark theme, providing a clean and simple user interface. The key technologies used in this project include:
* '''HTML''': used for structuring the content
* '''CSS''': used for styling the page

== Installation ==
To use this project, users can clone the repository from [GitHub] and open the '''HTML''' file in a web browser. No additional installation or setup is required.

